WEBVTT

00:00.401 --> 00:02.733
PREVIOUSLY
ON "GREY'S ANATOMY"...

00:02.733 --> 00:05.136
WE HAD SEX -- ONCE.
GO OUT WITH ME.

00:05.136 --> 00:07.408
YOU KNOW YOU'RE MY BOSS.
IT'S AGAINST THE RULES.

00:07.408 --> 00:10.211
DO YOU LIKE IZZIE?
IS THAT WHAT THIS IS ABOUT?

00:10.211 --> 00:11.682
SHE'S NOT THE ONE
I'M ATTRACTED TO.

00:11.682 --> 00:13.344
NOT THE ONE.
SO THERE'S A ONE.

00:13.344 --> 00:15.746
HAVEN'T YOU EVER BEEN ATTRACTED
TO SOMEONE YOU COULDN'T HAVE?

00:15.746 --> 00:18.049
MEREDITH.

00:18.049 --> 00:19.220
JUST COFFEE.

00:19.220 --> 00:20.221
GOOD.

00:20.221 --> 00:21.452
OKAY.
OKAY.

00:21.452 --> 00:23.624
BUT YOUR MOTHER'S ALZHEIMER'S
IS ADVANCING.

00:23.624 --> 00:25.556
WHILE SHE'S STILL
LUCID ENOUGH TO CONSENT,

00:25.556 --> 00:27.428
SHE NEEDS TO SIGN EVERYTHING
OVER TO YOU.

00:27.428 --> 00:29.330
ME?

00:29.330 --> 00:30.731
THANKS FOR THE COFFEE.

00:34.465 --> 00:36.807
Shepherd: SO, YOU BLEW ME OFF
FOR A BOTTLE OF TEQUILA.

00:36.807 --> 00:39.410
THAT'S NOT NEARLY AS MUCH FUN
TO WAKE UP TO.

00:39.410 --> 00:42.143
YOU MIND
MOVING THIS TAIL WAGON?

00:42.143 --> 00:43.414
YOU'RE BLOCKING ME IN.

00:44.775 --> 00:47.748
Grey:
A COUPLE HUNDRED YEARS AGO,

00:47.748 --> 00:50.521
BENJAMIN FRANKLIN SHARED
WITH THE WORLD

00:50.521 --> 00:52.283
THE SECRET OF HIS SUCCESS --

00:52.283 --> 00:55.526
"NEVER LEAVE THAT TILL
TOMORROW," HE SAID,

00:55.526 --> 00:57.057
"WHAT YOU CAN DO TODAY."

