NEVER CAME OUT.

19:04.374 --> 19:07.177
SO I PUT IT OFF.

19:09.249 --> 19:12.322
YOU KNOW, YOU'RE NOT THE
ONLY ONE...TO PUT THINGS OFF.

19:12.322 --> 19:15.225
