22:10.430 --> 22:13.503
ONCE THE PARKINSON'S PROGRESSES
TO A POINT OF DEMENTIA,

22:13.503 --> 22:15.565
YOU'RE NO LONGER
A CANDIDATE FOR DBS.

22:15.565 --> 22:18.067
