I'VE BEEN HOLDING 50 POUNDS
OF TUMOR FOR THE PAST 12 HOURS.

40:14.613 --> 40:18.617
MY BACK'S GONNA NEED TRACTION,
AND THE PATIENT DIED ANYWAYS.

40:18.617 --> 40:21.019
AND YOU THINK
YOU DID ME A FAVOR?

